          Fold the cup and insert gently while angling toward your lower back.
          Once placed correctly, it opens to form a secure, leak-resistant seal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STEP 3 -->
    <div class="fs-guide-row remove">
      <div class="fs-guide-img">
        <img src="{{ 'Meno-Cup--how-to-remove.jpg' | file_img_url: '800x' }}" alt="Remove menstrual cup">
