        <img src="{{ 'The-Don_t_s.jpg' | file_img_url: '800x' }}" alt="Menstrual cup do nots">
      </div>
      <div class="fs-guide-text">
        <h3>The Don’ts</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Avoid petroleum jelly or oil-based lubricants</li>
